FinTerms is an AI-powered Terms of Service review assistant for fintech startups. It helps founders identify risky clauses, understand potential consumer protection concerns across Washington, Oregon, and California, and generate clearer, safer contract language. Powered by RocketRide Cloud, FinTerms orchestrates a transparent review pipeline that analyzes agreements, ranks supporting citations, and suggests targeted rewrites—helping startups iterate on legal documents before seeking professional legal review.
